			Instant Alert Parent Notification		</h2>








<p style="text-align: left;">Inter-Lakes School District uses Instant Alert to notify parents when school is cancelled due to inclement weather or if there is critical information that we need to get to parents immediately. If you have school age children, it is important that you sign up for Instant Alert and keep your contact information current. Whether it is bad weather or an emergency, don't be the last to know, sign up for Instant Alert notifications from the School District: <a href="https://instantalert.honeywell.com">https://instantalert.honeywell.com</a></p>



